extendedInfo.description: - The VoterWeb is an app interface to my existing VoterWeb service. - This application is solely for the use of Pennsylvania Democratic committee members, progressive activists, and candidates I have taken as clients. - VoterWeb is NOT for the general public nor any registered Republicans. Any such access will be blocked or terminated upon detection.- This app may collect device information including, but not limited to, device phone number.- This is necessary to maintain security, identify users, allow me to proactively contact users, and block users violating any of my terms of use (previously stated or not).- VoterWeb is the most up-to-data online voter data resource in PA for Democrats and progressive grassroots activists.
